title: Episode 200: Lip Service Live Part 1 (Feat. Khadeen & Devale Ellis)
itunes:title: Episode 200: Lip Service Live Part 1 (Feat. Khadeen & Devale Ellis)
description:
Shouts to everyone who came out the live show! Khadeen and Devale Ellis joined the ladies of Lip Service again for this very special episode. The ladies start off by getting the crowd involved in all the fun, having guests explain their cheating stories. Khadeen and Devale play a game of "Is it Cheating If...," and much more! Part 2 with Trina will be out next week. Enjoy!
